\left|a_{n}\right|\leq A\frac{1-\left|\zn{x}{}\right|^{-n}}{\left|\zn{x}{}\right|-1}\stackrel{\left|\zn{x}{}\right|>1}{\quad\leq\quad}A\frac{1}{\left|\zn{x}{}\right|-1}\]

\end_inset 


